Procedure*Text: In this section, you will be presented with a series of words. Please study each word carefully. Your memory will be tested! Click next to continue.

After studying each set of words, you will be asked to rate your ability to remember all of the words on a later test. You will make these ratings using a scale of 0 to 100. A rating of 0 = WILL NOT REMEMBER, while a rating of 100 = WILL DEFINITELY REMEMBER. Please try to be as accurate as possible with these ratings!
You will now begin the study. Click next when you are ready to begin.
You have completed this section. Please click next to continue.
